snippet.title: American Truck Simulator - Nebraska
snippet.description:
Get ready to explore & haul a variety of loads through Nebraska in American Truck Simulator. Discover hidden gems, local industries, history, culture, cities, and more on the road ahead! 

Ready to go? Add it to your Steam Wishlist TODAY!
